description: Slider House Burger Co. has rolled out onto the streets of San Diego with a host of delicious gourmet sliders on the menu! Get your signature beef patty topped with a number of eclectic toppings (which include quail eggs, fried spam strips, and prosciutto) or go for the mouth-watering BBQ pulled pork slider. Oh and of course, no order would be complete without a side of fries.
name: Slider House Burger Co.
